body:
### Welcome to josephcaudle.com
Perhaps you've come here by accident or perhaps you meant to show up here, but whichever it is, welcome! There isn't much here now, but you can find some of what I do on [GitHub](http://github.com/jcaudle) or by perusing [my employer's site](http://www.squaremouth.com).

I also [tweet](http://twitter.com/josephcaudle) and might do some blogging some time soon.
